comments: Harris (PHI) places a hand to the front of Hart (NOP), but does not affect his FOM off-ball.

Ingram (NOP) makes contact to Embiid's (PHI) arm during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.

Simmons (PHI) makes contact to Ingram's (NOP) arm during his shooting motion that affects his jump shot attempt.
